---
title: HelloHero: Pork Schnitzel & Herby Mash with Garlicky Veggies & Garlic Hollandaise
description: Here's a neat trick: when you're crumbing food, use one hand for the wet ingredients and the other for the dry so you don't end
up with fingers that look like hotdogs! Give it a try when you make these golden pork schnitzels.
